Authors@R: 
    person("Tim", "Riffe", , "tim.riffe@ehu.eus", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates state survivorships and occupancy times by age from discrete time transition probabilities blazingly fast and without matrix inversion. State spaces are flexibly supported, and input formats are also flexible (lists, data.frames, matrices)
